milestones.description: Niall O'Brien has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (5) in ODIs for IRE, going past Poynter's 4
Ghulam Shabber has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (4) in ODIs for UAE, going past Amjad Ali's 3
Naveed has broken the record for most sixes (12) in ODIs for UAE, going past Shaiman Anwar's 12
Zahoor Khan has taken the most five-wicket hauls (1) in ODIs for UAE, going past Dukanwala's record
Ahmed Raza has broken the record for most catches (9) in ODIs for UAE, going past Amjad Javed's 8
Porterfield has scored 23 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for IRE breaking Paul Stirling's record
